                <li><p> 🎯 <alert> Practice: </alert> Problems 2-24 (alternating evens) in Exercises 2.3 (pg. 60-61). </p></li> 
            </ol>
        </p>
    </subsection>
    

    <subsection>
        <title>2.4 - Substitution</title>
        <p>
            In this section, students will learn how to simplify first-order differential equations using substitution. 
